"implicit target name: \"memory safety\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_aos_array.py:134
msgid ""
"The mixin observes ``BufferChangedEvent`` from VTK.  If the underlying "
"buffer is reallocated (e.g. by ``SetNumberOfTuples``), the cached numpy view "
"is automatically invalidated to prevent use-after-free."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_aos_array.py:139
msgid ""
"Arithmetic/home/runner/work/vtk-docs-l10n/vtk-docs-l10n/out/repo/Wrapping/"
"Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_aos_array.py:139: (INFO/1) Duplicate "
"implicit target name: \"arithmetic\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_aos_array.py:141
msgid ""
"Element-wise operations (``+``, ``-``, ``*``, ``/``, comparisons, ufuncs) "
"produce new VTK-backed AOS arrays with metadata (``dataset``, "
"``association``) propagated.  Reductions (``sum``, ``mean``, etc.) return "
"plain scalars or numpy arrays."
msgstr ""

